            It's our responsibility to engage leads, qualify, follow up and schedule. By handling the back-and-forth, your staff has over 10 additional hours a week to focus on delivering great patient care.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <i class="ti ti-target"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Lead Quality Over Volume</h3>
          <p>
            We filter out 65% of leads and only book patients who are financially qualified and ready for treatment — which is why 75% of the consults we schedule convert to accepted cases.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="why-card">
